OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Organization
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: An organization is a unit of your client or legal entity - examples are store, department. You can share data between organizations.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Movement Date
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: The date that a certain item is moved from one location to another.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The Movement Date indicates the date that a product moved in or out of inventory. This is the result of a shipment, receipt or inventory movement.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Unit Cost
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: When checked the cost amount is considered part of the unit cost of the transaction or a cost added like freight costs or insurance costs.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: When checked the cost amount is considered part of the unit cost of the transaction or a cost added like freight costs or insurance costs.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Organization
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: An organization is a unit of your client or legal entity - examples are store, department. You can share data between organizations.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Product
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: An item produced by a process.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Identifies an item which is either purchased or sold in this organization.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Total Cost Amount
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: A charge related to conducting business.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Rate
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: The percentage to be multiplied by the source to arrive at the tax or exchange amount.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The Rate indicates the percentage to be multiplied by the source to arrive at the tax or exchange amount.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Incremental
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: When this flag is checked the amount entered in the cost field is added to the current cost of the transaction.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: When this flag is checked the amount entered in the cost field is added to the current cost of the transaction.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Fix Backdated From
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Starting date in the costing rule to fix backdated transactions
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Starting date in the costing rule to fix backdated transactions

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Is Matching adjusted
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: When checked the differences in the Matched documents are processed creating a Cost Adjustment

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Accounting Date
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: The date this transaction is recorded for in the general ledger.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The date this transaction is recorded on in the general ledger. This date also indicates which accounting period within the fiscal year this transaction will be part of.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Foreign Amount
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: Amount of transaction in foreign currency

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Currency
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: An accepted medium of monetary exchange that may vary across countries.
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: Indicates the currency to be used when processing this document.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: G/L Item
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: An alias for the Account Combination which can be commonly used in daily operations.

OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.NAME: Organization List
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.DESCRIPTION: List of Organizations this Role can access
OBUIAPP_PARAMETER.HELP: The Organization List indicates the Organizations (by organization id) that this Role can access. Multiple Organizations are delimited by a comma ','.
